hopobject.body: I'm in a band nexahealth.org The line of headpieces includes a bright blue wig modeled after one of pop star Katy Perry's many looks, and a platinum blond wig in the style of Lady Gaga, hair bow and all. Other favorites include a brunette bowl cut wig to complete your cat's Katie Holmes or Sharon Osbourne outfit, and some spiky hairpieces that can transform your pet into a punk rocker or, if you are crafty, a Muppet.
